    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器收集与武器培养放置游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>空闲</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自动获得武器、我的房间、点唱机、游戏币等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>武器</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据稀有度自动获得武器</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >稀有度：普通、稀有、传奇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最高等级：9999</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传奇武器随着升级展现出独特效果</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>喂食</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据稀有度自动获得喂食</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >稀有度：普通、稀有、传奇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用于武器升级</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>我的房间</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据稀有度自动获得我的房间</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >稀有度：普通、稀有、传奇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有各种主题的背景</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>点唱机</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据稀有度自动获得点唱机</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >稀有度：普通、稀有、传奇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >具有不同氛围的配乐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>商店</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >普通商店：允许购买普通和稀有物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传奇商店：允许购买传奇物品</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操作</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全屏/窗口模式：F4</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >默认键位：方向键、Enter、Esc、鼠标</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持自定义键位</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像照顾宝宝一样照顾武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它会感到饥饿并且会拉屎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以自動獲得傳奇武器。</p>",
